HEADWORD: Handspike
<hw>Hand"spike`</hw> <pr>(h⟦acr⟧nd"sp⟦imac⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>A bar or lever, generally of wood, used in a windlass or capstan,
